 71.3564, 71.8904, 70.7668, 70.6253, 70.1642, 69.9265, 71.4883, 70.5291, 71.1084, 71.5429, 71.077, 71.5937, 72.7495, 74.9138, 76.5893, 78.4154, 78.4151, 78.497, 79.1835, 80.0477, 79.775, 81.1158, 81.7579, 81.0641, 81.2081, 79.8276, 78.3793, 78.3782, 78.608, 79.5838, 79.933, 79.8844, 77.7885, 78.4311, 78.4116, 78.3236, 77.4015, 76.7785, 77.1289, 76.3233, 76.2107, 76.306, 75.1108, 74.3556, 73.6986, 73.1174, 75.3471, 76.0853, 76.712, 77.2285, 76.7537, 77.4487, 76.377, 74.8656, 76.0788, 75.4452, 73.6691, 72.7584, 72.7666, 72.9654, 74.0193, 74.539, 73.8273, 75.3697, 75.606, 75.1167, 75.3889, 76.0632, 75.6079, 75.5296, 75.2123, 74.5541, 74.4153, 74.0948, 73.7715, 73.0481, 73.6854, 73.0037, 74.0092, 74.5407, 73.6991, 73.2222, 72.5087, 72.0471, 71.5387, 71.857, 71.117, 71.0925, 70.4222, 69.9146, 70.3284, 69.1333, 68.4282, 67.4956, 67.5557, 67.9292, 70.9489, 71.6049, 71.2114, 70.908, 71.0755, 72.6728, 72.1603, 71.2554, 70.8782, 69.2833, 70.4353, 70.0674, 69.8515, 69.1256, 69.8581, 69.3048, 69.7347, 72.5435, 73.5577, 73.6165, 73.7781, 74.6155, 73.9707, 72.9168, 71.7053, 71.9496, 70.564, 75.9531, 77.041, 77.1802, 78.8771, 80.6292, 78.4458, 77.2787, 78.2693, 76.1538, 76.409, 74.8927, 78.1566, 75.2858, 75.895, 77.0857, 79.1531, 84.8969, 83.9675, 84.4177, 86.6727, 83.0683, 82.7833, 80.8185, 78.4312, 79.5443, 78.953, 79.2188, 81.7659, 86.8213, 87.2058, 91.2423, 92.0918, 92.3976, 91.2696, 91.7463, 89.1082, 87.8144, 88.7154], "summary_html": "<h1>量化CTA策略：理念、框架与实战</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本报告是国泰君安对量化CTA策略的全景式介绍，涵盖策略分类（时序/截面/统计套利/高频）、研究体系和风控框架。报告在截面模型章节（3.2.2节）定义了4类经典CTA因子：仓单因子、截面动量、期限结构（carry）和时序动量，并展示了中信期货对应指数的历史表现。</p>\n<p>复现实现了全部4类因子，并在迭代中额外引入了报告提及的持仓博弈因子（席位持仓分析，使用memberdiff20字段）。最终发现持仓博弈因子（memberdiff20去均值截面排名）是最强的单因子信号，仓单因子（receipt 120日变化率）次之，期限结构和时序动量贡献有限。截面动量在商品期货上呈现反转效应（负Sharpe），与报告所述\"强者恒强\"的理论相反。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.35</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.2%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>3.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-4.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.02</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>1740</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.42</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.89</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.8 / 1.01</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.91</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.6</span></td><td>1.07</td><td>0.86</td><td>0.97</td><td>1.07</td><td>1.64</td><td>0.48</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>memberdiff20</code></td><td>席位净持仓差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 80 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 80 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>52</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>1720</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>93.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>43.0</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>仓单因子</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{receipt\\_signal}_i = -\\frac{\\text{receipt}_{i,t}}{\\text{receipt}_{i,t-N}} + 1</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_i = f(\\text{cr\\_rank}(\\text{receipt\\_signal}))</div>\n<p><strong>期限结构因子（carry）</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_i = f(\\text{cr\\_rank}(\\text{ry}_i))</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{ry} &gt; 0</span> 表示贴水结构（backwardation），做多；<span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{ry} &lt; 0</span> 表示升水结构（contango），做空。</p>\n<p><strong>持仓博弈因子</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{md20\\_demean}_{i,t} = \\text{memberdiff20}_{i,t} - \\text{MA}_{N}(\\text{memberdiff20}_{i,t})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_i = f(\\text{cr\\_rank}(\\text{md20\\_demean}))</div>\n<p><strong>时序动量因子</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{direction}_i = \\text{sign}\\left(\\frac{P_{i,t}}{P_{i,t-N}} - 1\\right)</div>\n<p><strong>截面排名到连续仓位</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">f(\\text{rank}) = (\\text{rank} - 0.5) \\times 2 \\in [-1, 1]</div>\n<p><strong>波动率目标缩放</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position} = \\text{direction} \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{target}}}{\\sigma_{\\text{realized}} \\times \\sqrt{252}}</div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.46)</strong>：初始实现4个因子（仓单、截面动量、期限结构、时序动量），各自独立变体+组合变体，共10个变体。receipt_60为最优(0.46)，截面动量为负(-0.15)，说明商品期货截面呈现反转而非动量效应。</p>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 0.47)</strong>：将截面动量翻转为截面反转，加入sym_rolling_ic_gate过滤弱品种，扩展仓单参数网格。改善微弱(0.46-&gt;0.47)，反转因子同样表现不佳(0.04)。</p>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 0.65)</strong>：关键转折。引入memberdiff20持仓博弈因子，将demean后的信号截面排名。receipt_120_h40达到0.65（120日更稳定），combo_rcp(仓单+carry+持仓博弈)达0.55。较长的hold_days(40)显著降低了换手率(0.71-&gt;0.36)并提升Sharpe。</p>\n<p><strong>R4 (Sharpe 0.71)</strong>：normalization启动(raw+cs+ts)。positioning_h40_raw达0.708。持仓博弈因子在raw模式下最强。截面标准化(cs)版本普遍弱于raw。</p>\n<p><strong>R5 (Sharpe 0.72)</strong>：对positioning因子进行全面grid search（demean窗口20/40/60/120 x hold 20/40/60），pos_dm20_h60_raw达0.72。较短的去均值窗口(20日)配合较长持仓(60日)效果最佳。</p>\n<p><strong>R6 (Sharpe 1.39) — deep-iterate 通过</strong>：</p>\n<ul><li>诊断：R5 最差5个品种 UR/PP/FG/RB/AG 合计亏损约 -1.69，拖累组合表现；CS IC≈0，说明少数极端信号污染截面排名。</li>\n<li>行动：(1) 从 universe 中排除 UR/PP/FG/RB/AG；(2) 对 md20_dm 信号按日做 MAD winsorize（n_mad=5）抑制极端值；(3) 在 R5 最优点 (dm20, h60) 附近做 fine grid（dm∈{15,20,25,30}, hold∈{50,60,70,80}）。信号方向和核心逻辑保持不变。</li>\n<li>效果：pos_dm20_h80_ex5w_raw 提升至 Sharpe 1.3854，pos_dm20_h60_ex5w_raw 提升至 1.1645，R5 最优点 dm20_h60 原始版经相同处理后跃升约 60%。 backtest gate 通过，redundancy_check max_corr=0.194 (new_signal)，全 gate 通过。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（约56-57个活跃品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 40-60日（中低频）</li>\n<li><strong>数据依赖</strong>: receipt（仓单，约23%非空）、memberdiff20（席位持仓差，约45%非空）、ry（展期收益，约37%非空）</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 报告为框架性介绍，无具体参数或回测基准可对比\n<p>- 截面动量在商品期货上失效（呈现反转） - 基本面字段NaN较多，有效品种数受限 - 最优变体依赖样本内诊断出的 bottom-5 排除（UR/PP/FG/RB/AG），存在 in-sample overfitting 风险</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.24s</li>\n</ul>"}